caption.p: Molecular dynamics simulations analysis of docked (M pro – Remdesivir) and native (M pro– N3 peptide) complexes of 2019-nCoV M pro during 100 ns period (A) RMSD plot of the docked and native (B) RMSF of docked and native (C) Radius of Gyration (rGyr) of docked and native complexes (D) Solvent Accessible Surface Area (SASA) of docked (M pro – Remdesivir) (E) SASA of docked (M pro– N3 peptide).
